    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903880/extras/c33d2a89df66b002d153ecc1ccd40057.avif?t=1647274696\" width=616 height=82 /></span><br>The sheep are hungry!<br><br>But they don't know how to find the grass on their own.<br>Push them to the grass so they can eat.<br>But be careful, you don't want one getting in the way of the other.<br><br>Push the sheep is a game where you have to think to solve the puzzles and proceed to the next level.<br><br>Each level more challenging than the next, and don't be fooled by the childish graphics, only the greatest geniuses are able to make it to the end.<br><br>Push all the sheep into each bush to win the stage.<br>You can only push, never pull, but don't worry, you still can undo every move you made.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903880/extras/eb682af43ab3cc1b94cb3e9ba339e1af.poster.avif?t=1647274696\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903880/extras/eb682af43ab3cc1b94cb3e9ba339e1af.webm?t=1647274696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903880/extras/eb682af43ab3cc1b94cb3e9ba339e1af.mp4?t=1647274696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
